Since you are already using tap-hold for your home row mods, you can add Escape to one of your home row keys. Many Vim users put Escape on a "pinky tap."

For example, you could modify your a key:

Tap: a

Hold: lctl

Tap with another key (Combo): esc (or just use a different key altogether).

